elements of the sequence, sorted using the given predicate as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the comparison between elements."}]},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift":{"type":"topic","title":"Swift","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Build apps using a powerful open language."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"/documentation/swift","role":"collection","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift"}}}